dynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/113129/', '[1] "Product Information. Plegridy (peginterferon beta-1a)." Biogen Idec Inc, Cambridge, MA.[2] "Product Information. Betaseron (interferon beta-1b)." Berlex, Richmond, CA.[3] "Product Information. Rebif (interferon beta-1a)." Serono Laboratories Inc, Norwell, MA.[4] "Product Information. Avonex (interferon beta-1a)." Biogen, Cambridge, MA.', 'Interferon alfa-n1, Oprelvekin, Sipuleucel-T, Elapegademase, Peginterferon alfa-2a, Ropeginterferon alfa-2b, Interferon alfacon-1, Sargramostim, Histamine, Aldesleukin, Pegademase, More', 'Capreomycin, Rifamycin, Rifapentine, Streptomycin, Trimethoprim, Cycloserine, Rifabutin, Pyridoxine, Pretomanid, Trimethoprim, Tamsulosin, More', 1767369485);
